{
  "id": "cli/cache",
  "title": "ng cache",
  "contents": "\n<article>\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n      \"itemListElement\": [\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli\", \"name\": \"CLI\" } },\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli/cache\", \"name\": \"cache\" } }\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n    <a href=\"cli\">CLI</a>\n</div>\n\n  \n<header class=\"cli-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"ng-cache\">ng cache<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/cache#ng-cache\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n</header>\n\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"cli-body\">\n    <p>Configure persistent disk cache and retrieve cache statistics.</p>\n\n    \n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng <span class=\"cli-name\">cache</span>\n</code-example>\n\n\n\n    \n    <h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"----------code--------description----\">\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/tree/refs/heads/17.3.x/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/cache/long-description.md\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n        Description\n    </h2>\n    <p>Angular CLI saves a number of cachable operations on disk by default.</p>\n<p>When you re-run the same build, the build system restores the state of the previous build and re-uses previously performed operations, which decreases the time taken to build and test your applications and libraries.</p>\n<p>To amend the default cache settings, add the <code>cli.cache</code> object to your <a href=\"guide/workspace-config\">Workspace Configuration</a>.\nThe object goes under <code>cli.cache</code> at the top level of the file, outside the <code>projects</code> sections.</p>\n<code-example language=\"jsonc\">\n{\n  \"$schema\": \"./node_modules/@angular/cli/lib/config/schema.json\",\n  \"version\": 1,\n  \"cli\": {\n    \"cache\": {\n      // ...\n    }\n  },\n  \"projects\": {}\n}\n</code-example>\n<p>For more information, see <a href=\"guide/workspace-config#cache-options\">cache options</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"cache-environments\">Cache environments<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/cache#cache-environments\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p>By default, disk cache is only enabled for local environments. The value of environment can be one of the following:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>all</code> - allows disk cache on all machines.</li>\n<li><code>local</code> - allows disk cache only on development machines.</li>\n<li><code>ci</code> - allows disk cache only on continuous integration (CI) systems.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To change the environment setting to <code>all</code>, run the following command:</p>\n<code-example language=\"bash\">\nng config cli.cache.environment all\n</code-example>\n<p>For more information, see <code>environment</code> in <a href=\"guide/workspace-config#cache-options\">cache options</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p>The Angular CLI checks for the presence and value of the <code>CI</code> environment variable to determine in which environment it is running.</p>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"cache-path\">Cache path<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/cache#cache-path\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p>By default, <code>.angular/cache</code> is used as a base directory to store cache results.</p>\n<p>To change this path to <code>.cache/ng</code>, run the following command:</p>\n<code-example language=\"bash\">\nng config cli.cache.path \".cache/ng\"\n</code-example>\n\n    \n\n    \n    <p>This command has the following <a href=\"cli/cache#cache-commands\">sub-commands</a>:</p><p>\n    </p><ul>\n      \n      <li><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"cli/cache#clean-command\">clean</a></li>\n      \n      <li><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"cli/cache#disable-command\">disable</a></li>\n      \n      <li><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"cli/cache#enable-command\">enable</a></li>\n      \n      <li><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"cli/cache#info-command\">info</a></li>\n      \n    </ul>\n    \n\n    \n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"options\">Options</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th style=\"width:15%\">Option</th>\n      <th style=\"width:40%\">Description</th>\n      <th>Value Type</th>\n      <th>Default Value</th>\n      </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax no-auto-link\">--help</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        \n        <p>Shows a help message for this command in the console.</p>\n\n        \n      </td>\n      <td><code class=\"no-auto-link\">boolean</code></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n<h2 id=\"cache-commands\"><a id=\"cache-commands\"></a>Cache commands<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/cache#cache-commands\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"clean\"><a id=\"clean-command\"></a>clean<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/cache#clean\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng cache <span class=\"cli-name\">clean</span>\n</code-example>\n\n\n<p>Deletes persistent disk cache from disk.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"disable\"><a id=\"disable-command\"></a>disable<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/cache#disable\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng cache <span class=\"cli-name\">disable</span>\n</code-example>\n\n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng cache <span class=\"cli-name\">off</span>\n</code-example>\n\n\n<p>Disables persistent disk cache for all projects in the workspace.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"enable\"><a id=\"enable-command\"></a>enable<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/cache#enable\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng cache <span class=\"cli-name\">enable</span>\n</code-example>\n\n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng cache <span class=\"cli-name\">on</span>\n</code-example>\n\n\n<p>Enables disk cache for all projects in the workspace.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"info\"><a id=\"info-command\"></a>info<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/cache#info\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"api-heading no-auto-link\">\n  ng cache <span class=\"cli-name\">info</span>\n</code-example>\n\n\n<p>Prints persistent disk cache configuration and statistics in the console.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/workspace-config\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - cli/cache#cache-commands\n - cli/cache#cache-environments\n - cli/cache#cache-path\n - cli/cache#clean\n - cli/cache#clean-command\n - cli/cache#disable\n - cli/cache#disable-command\n - cli/cache#enable\n - cli/cache#enable-command\n - cli/cache#info\n - cli/cache#info-command\n - cli/cache#ng-cache\n - guide/workspace-config\n - guide/workspace-config#cache-options\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/tree/refs/heads/17.3.x/packages/angular/cli/src/commands/cache/long-description.md\n-->"
